<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>THE STORY OF CALVARY</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Thumak ka gen chim theihloh chuh,
 Kalvari chanchin ahi;
 Bangti'n a, Pathien Cha chang khat,
 Gilo kei di'n A hung thih?

[V2]
 Kalvari tang
 Ka ngaihtuoh tawp thei puoh ie!

[V3]
 2. Nanghaw van Angel thiengtho leh,
 Serafim lopite haw;
 Nichenga Lalpa nasem leh,
 A deihguol thil bawl sek haw.

[V4]
 Kalvari tang
 Chanchin nei hih thei puou maw?

[V5]
 3. Aw, ka thagau zie tang achun,
 Sun, zanin va leng zingin;
 Na Lalpa kross leka um chuh,
 A hingin va mun na tin.

[V6]
 Kalvari tang
 Chanchin hun na hilh ina.

[V7]
 4. Sim leh Mal, Sak leh Thang a um,
 A keng bulah khun u hen;
 A tek-akhang, alien-aneu,
 A min pakin la sau hen.

[V8]
 Kalvari-ah
 Amau din A thawk ziekin.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>128</hymn_number>
</song>